ribedby="caption-attachment-3488702" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3488702" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic.jpg" alt="妮莉·费塔多、贾斯汀·汀布莱克和提姆巴兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Nelly-Furtado-Justin-Timberlake-and-Timbaland.-Credit-Chris-Polk_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488702" class="wp-caption-text">妮莉·费塔多、贾斯汀·汀布莱克和提姆巴兰。图片来源：Chris Polk/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>今年早些时候，提姆巴兰证实他的长期合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/timbaland-confirms-justin-timberlake-has-finished-up-his-next-album-3429583">汀布莱克已经完成了他的下一张专辑</a>。</p><p>本月早些时候，Timbaland<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/timbaland-collaborator-magoo-has-died-tributes-3482805">向他的长期合作者兼说唱歌手 Magoo 致敬</a>，后者去世，享年 50 岁。Magoo 最出名的是作为 1989 年成立的 Timbaland 和 Magoo 二人组的一员。两人在青少年时期相识并发行了首张专辑1997 年的《Welcome To Our World》催生了热门歌曲《Up Jumps Da Boogie》。</p><p> Timbaland &amp; Magoo 也将成为 Da Bassment Cru 集体的一部分，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">Missy Elliott</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ginuwine">Ginuwine</a>和 Playa。 Magoo 还<a href="https://youknowigotsoul.com/magoo-interview-connecting-with-timbaland-reflecting-on-da-bassment-leaving-music-career-behind" target="_blank" rel="noopener">因将 Missy Elliott 介绍给 Timbaland 而受到赞誉</a>，两人后来形成了一场改变流派的合作。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/timbaland-release-date-new-single-nelly-furtado-justin-timberlake-3489538">Timbaland 宣布与 Nelly Furtado 和 Justin Timberlake 合作的新单曲发行日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
